701193f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - Van Cortlandt Avenue
701193f-a.text:
Grand Concourse, west side, north from but not including Van Cortlandt
Ave., to and including East Mosholu Parkway South. Also shown is the
elevated structure of the I.R.T. Van Cortlandt Park subway line running
on Jerome Ave.
May 8, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
